      "content": "that's a good start. can u expand on the part about \"structural inequities\"? i want to make sure i really nail the part where i explain why the traditional idea of meritocracy doesn't actually work in this context. how can i frame meritocracy as being fundamentally broken or even harmful when it comes to racial equity?",
